snippet.title: Amber Heard Under FBI Investigation
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Under FBI Investigation
Subscribe Here 👉 http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3GGGFNX

Amber Heard’s old dog-smuggling scandal has come back to bite her. According to reports she is now the subject of investigation by an FBI-backed probe regarding allegations of perjury. She is still expected to go to trial next year with Johnny Depp, but this investigation may cause her some problems.
